The collection of your data is subject to this privacy policy.

Information collected:
Country as defined in your Spotify account data,
Spotify premium status.

This information is stored locally on your computer and is never transmitted from it by this software.
Once you close Arma 3 this information is no longer avaliable on your computer.

This software including the relevent webpage used for authorisation does not use cookies.
No third parties place cookies in your browser to collect information about your browsering information through this software and the relevent webpage used for authorisation.
